kind: llman.sdd.delta
ops[2]{op,req_id,title,statement,from,to,name}:
  add_requirement,r1,"ngram-detection","System MUST detect repetitive token loops via sliding window n-gram analysis and interrupt generation.",null,null,null
  add_requirement,r2,"recovery-chain",System MUST attempt configurable recovery strategies (alter_prompt switch_model adjust_params delegate_to_planner) in sequence.,null,null,null
op_scenarios[2]{req_id,id,given,when,then}:
  r1,happy,a mock model outputs repeated token pattern,detection threshold is exceeded,generation is interrupted and recovery triggered
  r2,happy,recovery alter_prompt fails,switch_model strategy is attempted,model is switched to alternate provider (OpenAI ↔ Anthropic)
